title: Denver the last dinosaur. 4. Winning!
brief_description: Legends of dinosaurs have for centuries enchanted children of all ages, but Denver is the most endearing dinosaur personality ever. In this adventure, Denver and Jeremy enter a wacky game show only to find they’re competing against the team of Morton Fizzback and Professor Funt.
